lead_paragraph: Mementos from the soccer world that brought Syrian refugee Osama Abdul Mohsen to Spain are strewn around the flat he shares with two of his sons, including a ball signed by Real Madrid's star players and a banner for the local team, Getafe.

headline.print_headline: Syrian Whose Plight Went Viral Finds Refuge in Spanish Soccer
